The Irish Sea is a [[sea]] in the [[British Isles]] between the islands of [[Great Britain]] and [[Ireland]].

It is boardered to the north by the [[North Channel]] and to the south by [[St. George's Channel]] and the [[Celtic Sea]].

The Irish Sea is part of the soverign territories of the [[United Kingdom]], the [[Republic of Ireland]] and the [[Isle of Man]] - an island nation in the centre of the Irish Sea.

